            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米早前在 MWC，除了推出了全新的 15 Ultra 手機外，還推出了不少新品，全新的入門旗艦平板 Pad 7 Pro 就是其中一分子。回到香港，Edward 借得這部平板並試玩了數星期，現在就為大家分享一下詳細的試用感受吧。</p><h2>小米 Pad 7 Pro 開箱直擊</h2><p>在為大家分享小米最新推出的 Pad 7 Pro 平板的使用體驗前，先讓 Edward 為大家帶來它的開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299921" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是小米最新推出 Pad 7 Pro 平板的包裝盒，採用全白色簡約設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者測試的是藍色版本，規格為 12GB RAM + 512GB 內存版本，屬於最高階的配置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包裝盒上標明小米 Pad 7 Pro 採用了 HyperOS 2 作業系統，並支援 Dolby「全餐」，即同時支援 Dolby Vision 及 Dolby Atmos。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打開包裝盒，就會見到 Pad 7 Pro 包裝在紙質包裝袋內。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拿起平板就會見到底部有一個白色紙盒，內藏 USB-A to USB-C 數據電源線及説明書，值得留意的是它並未附送充電火牛。</p><h2>設計與上代相近手感亦似</h2><p>相比上代 Pad 6s Pro，今代小米 Pad 7 Pro 在設計上大致維持相同風格，機身同樣是採用一體化金屬物料製造，機面亦是一塊屏佔比甚高的熒幕，不過今代就加入了更多清新顏色，相比上代只設石墨灰一種商務感較重的顏色，今代除了灰色外，亦設有藍色及綠色機身，Edward 手上的就是藍色機款，配上金屬質感，無論觀感還是手感都算不錯。另外，今代熒幕細了，但機身亦薄了及輕了，所以外攜使用時手感十分不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者借得的是藍色版本，外表上頗為漂亮，而機身就採用了一體化金屬物料製造，十分硬淨。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身採用平邊圓角設計，感覺就像一塊四圓角磚頭。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過它的機身十分輕薄，厚度只有 6.18mm，而淨機身重量亦僅 502.8g，以一部 11 吋熒幕平板來説外攜方便性算高。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過由於機身頗橫身，所以橫向單手拿機，長時間仍會覺得較重。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果單手直向拿機，手感不但較舒服，用來瀏覽文件或網頁亦會更自然及舒服一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身設計方面，基本上與上代 Pad 6s Pro 差不多，機背右上角仍設有 5,000 萬像素主攝鏡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而機面熒幕頂部中央位置亦設有 3,200 萬像素自拍鏡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按鍵方面，機身左側頂部設有開關鍵，而機頂左側就設有音量鍵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而開關鍵亦有內建指紋辨識器，解鎖裝置十分方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而機身右側就設有 USB-C 插槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而介面方面，它採用了 HyperOS 2 介面，操作上與其他採用相同 OS 的小米手機或平板差不多。</p><br /><b>
]]>
